"'''When U Cry I Cry'''" is a song performed by [[Jesse Campbell (singer)|Jesse Campbell]] (then known as '''Jesse'''), issued as the lead [[single (music)|single]] from his debut album ''Never Let You Go''. The song peaked at #29 on the ''[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]'' [[Hot R&B/Hip-Hop Songs|R&B]] chart in 1995.<ref name="allmusic">{{cite web|url=http://www.allmusic.com/artist/jesse-campbell-mn0000331133/awards|title=Jesse Campbell - Awards - AllMusic|work=[[AllMusic]]|accessdate=April 28, 2014}}</ref>

